<div class="content" name="SiteInformationBLOB" uuid="2354d145-9283-48f2-85e6-57288eb1b2e6"><p>The SiteInformationBLOB contains the mapping from a <a href="a9bc4403-a862-48b9-b99b-1b44a887d177#gt_a2c6d1c9-deea-427c-91ee-56f6e726eabd" data-linktype="relative-path">DFS target</a> <a href="a9bc4403-a862-48b9-b99b-1b44a887d177#gt_fe6fd875-b30a-44bb-850e-10733990f04c" data-linktype="relative-path">host name</a> to its site name.
There MUST be no more than one <a href="a9bc4403-a862-48b9-b99b-1b44a887d177#gt_ad861812-8cb0-497a-80bb-13c95aa4e425" data-linktype="relative-path">BLOB</a> of this type. This
BLOB contains zero or more <a href="9c4f5fef-b3fc-49a6-9afd-d30ee91a440c" data-linktype="relative-path">SiteEntryBLOBs</a>.</p><table>
