identifies the SiteInformationBLOB.</p><p><b>SiteEntryCount (4 bytes): </b>The number of
SiteEntryBLOBs in the SiteEntryBLOB field, stored as an unsigned, 32-bit, <a href="a9bc4403-a862-48b9-b99b-1b44a887d177#gt_079478cb-f4c5-4ce5-b72b-2144da5d2ce7" data-linktype="relative-path">little-endian</a> integer. This
MAY be zero.<a id="Appendix_A_Target_17"></a><a aria-label="Product behavior note 17" href="3a466440-1ef6-4439-b4e2-be9eaddeb511#Appendix_A_17" data-linktype="relative-path">&lt;17&gt;</a><a id="Appendix_A_Target_18"></a><a aria-label="Product behavior note 18" href="3a466440-1ef6-4439-b4e2-be9eaddeb511#Appendix_A_18" data-linktype="relative-path">&lt;18&gt;</a></p><p><b>SiteEntryBLOB (variable): </b>Zero or more BLOBs.
Each BLOB contains the site of a root target or link target server in the <a href="a9bc4403-a862-48b9-b99b-1b44a887d177#gt_6a3f0be9-b9b4-49df-9d1c-a3b89e4e9890" data-linktype="relative-path">DFS namespace</a>.</p></div>